response.original_title: SUPER☆GiRLSデビュー14周年記念ワンマンライブ～こんなスパガは今だけ、そうでしょ～
response.overview: Solo live concert to celebrate the 14th anniversary of the Japanese idol group SUPER☆GiRLS debut. The concert was held at Otemachi Mitsui Hall on December 22, 2024.  The set list included not only popular songs from SUPER☆GiRLS, but also some famous songs from iDOL Street and the first performances of new songs!  They had two performances on the same day. This day performance and a Christmas party that was held in the evening.
response.title: SUPER☆GiRLSデビュー14周年記念ワンマンライブ～こんなスパガは今だけ、そうでしょ～
